@startuml memory_hierarchy_overview
skinparam dpi 300
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft YaHei"

skinparam rectangle {
    BorderColor #333333
    BackgroundColor white
    FontStyle bold
}

rectangle "CPU寄存器" as Register #FFCCCC {
    note bottom: <1ns 访问延迟
}

rectangle "L1缓存(32-64KB)" as L1 #FFDDCC {
    note bottom: 1-3ns 访问延迟
}

rectangle "L2缓存(256KB-1MB)" as L2 #FFEECC {
    note bottom: 3-10ns 访问延迟
}

rectangle "L3缓存(数MB)" as L3 #FFFFCC {
    note bottom: 10-40ns 访问延迟
}

rectangle "主内存(RAM)" as RAM #EEFFCC {
    note bottom: 50-100ns 访问延迟
}

rectangle "固态硬盘(SSD)" as SSD #DDFFCC {
    note bottom: 10-100μs 访问延迟
}

rectangle "机械硬盘(HDD)" as HDD #CCFFCC {
    note bottom: 1-10ms 访问延迟
}

Register -down-> L1 : 数据流动
L1 -down-> L2 : 数据流动
L2 -down-> L3 : 数据流动
L3 -down-> RAM : 数据流动
RAM -down-> SSD : 数据流动
SSD -down-> HDD : 数据流动

note right of Register : 速度最快\n容量最小
note right of HDD : 速度最慢\n容量最大

@enduml 